      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，SRC节点代表Retail_PointOfSale，然后通过INGEST动作连到Retail_CouponSystem。我先把这条主线画出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SRC",
        "INGEST",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
