      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "优惠券系统收到数据后要做个校验，分出RAWVAL这个判断节点。校验通过和失败要走不同分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RAWVAL",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在Retail_CouponSystem后面加了RAWVAL菱形判断框。接下来PASS分支和FAIL分支分别指向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RAWVAL",
